{"tid":2368271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗批評美方行為霸凌　制裁帶來一些不便沒大不了","createTime":"2021-01-16T05:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T05:47:53.000Z","uid":283021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"492f5825f69107c36d5e182c9bd49ba35c21526d","tid":2368271,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:04:12.000Z","msg":"美國財政部因應香港問題再制裁多6人，包括全國人大常委譚耀宗。譚耀宗接受訪問時表示，從來沒有資產在美國，他之前已預料會這樣，批評美國的行為霸凌及干預香港事務。他強調為香港大局及繁榮穩定做事，是正義、合情、合理和合法，即使美國採取所謂的制裁措施為他帶來一些不便都沒有大不了。<br />\n<br />\n今次的制裁名單還有警方國安處人員，譚耀宗說，執法人員按照香港法例做事，不應該有制裁行動，亦與美國無關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570749-20210116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570749-20210116.htm&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=beb194a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570749-20210116.htm&h=f079c2ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570749-20210116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"99a4a03373f0e7d255fcba8416d468664470ef54","tid":2368271,"uid":283021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"因為淨翻無幾多年可以制裁"},{"pid":"8df1706cf0322de794170535586450e8cb453089","tid":2368271,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:11:07.000Z","msg":"你人大黎架嘛<br />\n咪動議反制裁囉, 唔係唔戰狼下話?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d8f0eef5b7ff1c51d35e4bcdbf6295b2c31797","tid":2368271,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"全家世世代代留在大灣區咪好方便囉"},{"pid":"710980a6e17a42f88d3c844ef8071e375022dfd4","tid":2368271,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"冇不便有咩好批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a6c6d6b1d2cf21fb7ff90